# Global Electronics Retail Analytics

## Business Problem

A global electronics retailer operates across multiple countries, stores, customers, and product categories.

The objective of this project is to:

- Analyze sales performance
- Evaluate store efficiency
- Identify top-performing products
- Track revenue growth trends
- Generate business recommendations using data-driven insights

## Tools Used

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Jupyter Notebook

## Dataset

The analysis combines:

- Sales
- Customers
- Products
- Stores
- Exchange Rates

Data Pre-processing and Dataset Overview shown below:

